{"type":"message","id":"362d3c35","parentId":"d6aae193","timestamp":"2026-03-29T03:10:59.639Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d3792c69d6848872ca00fd43c4d2c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>英语学习：美股新闻 | 英语学习博客</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"通过美股新闻学习英语词汇，包括抛售、通胀、暴跌等金融英语\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"../\" class=\"logo\">🎙️ MingoX</a>\n            <div class=\"nav-links\">\n                <a href=\"../\">首页</a>\n                <a href=\"../about.html\">关于</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <article class=\"post-content\">\n                    <h1>📚 英语学习：美股新闻</h1>\n\n                    <p><strong>US Stock</strong> <span class=\"english-word\">Sell-off</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.抛售）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Devastates</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.重创，现在时）</span> <strong>Tech Giants</strong></p>\n\n                    <p>最近一周，<span class=\"english-word\">Persistent</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.持续的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Inflation</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.通胀）</span>持续 <span class=\"english-word\">Surging</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.飙升，现在分词）</span>，市场 <span class=\"english-word\">Concerned</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.担心的）</span>利率会在更长时间内保持 <span class=\"english-word\">Elevated</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.升高的）</span>。大型科技股遭遇 <span class=\"english-word\">Severe</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.严重的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Setback</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.挫折）</span>，\"美股七巨头\"整体市值累计 <span class=\"english-word\">Evaporated</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.蒸发，过去式）</span>超过 8500 亿美元。</p>\n\n                    <p>Meta 本周 <span class=\"english-word\">Plunged</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.暴跌，过去式）</span>超 11%，创下自 2025 年 10 月以来最差 <span class=\"english-word\">Weekly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.每周的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Performance</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.表现）</span>。此前该公司在一桩 <span class=\"english-word\">Landmark</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.标志性的）</span>社交媒体 <span class=\"english-word\">Lawsuit</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.诉讼案）</span>中败诉。陪审团裁定 Meta 和谷歌 <span class=\"english-word\">Negligent</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.疏忽的）</span>，未能保护平台上的未成年用户。Alphabet 周内 <span class=\"english-word\">Declined</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.下降，过去式）</span>近 9%。</p>\n\n                    <p>微软下跌 6.5%，可能迎来 2008 年以来最差 <span class=\"english-word\">Quarterly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.季度的）</span>表现，软件股受冲击 <span class=\"english-word\">Particularly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adv.特别地）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Severe</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.严重的）</span>。英伟达和亚马逊均下跌约 3%，特斯拉五个交易日内 <span class=\"english-word\">Dropped</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.下跌，过去式）</span>近 2%。</p>\n\n                    <p>此次抛售潮前，Alphabet <span class=\"english-word\">Released</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.发布，过去式）</span>新的研究，公布了一款旨在降低 AI 内存占用的 <span class=\"english-word\">Algorithm</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.算法）</span>，引发 <span class=\"english-word\">Semiconductor</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.半导体）</span>板块 <span class=\"english-word\">Volatility</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.震荡）</span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>受油价 <span class=\"english-word\">Surge</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.飙升）</span>推高 <span class=\"english-word\">Inflationary</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.通胀的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Expectations</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.预期）</span>、债券收益率 <span class=\"english-word\">Rising</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.上升的）</span>影响，成长股本周遭 <span class=\"english-word\">Battered</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.重创，过去式/被动语态）</span>。投资者认为，<span class=\"english-word\">Federal</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.联邦的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Reserve</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.储备）</span>将无法按预期在今年 <span class=\"english-word\">Cut</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.降息，原形）</span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>苹果是\"美股七巨头\"中唯一 <span class=\"english-word\">Modest</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.适度的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Gain</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.涨幅）</span>的个股。报道称，苹果计划将 Siri 语音助手 <span class=\"english-word\">Open</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.开放，原形/不定式）</span>给 ChatGPT 之外的其他 <span class=\"english-word\">Competing</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.竞争的）</span> AI <span class=\"english-word\">Service</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.服务）</span>。</p>\n                </article>\n\n                <!-- 词汇表 -->\n                <div class=\"subtitle\">📖 词汇表</div>\n                <table class=\"vocab-table\">\n                    <thead>\n                        <tr><th>单词</th><th>词性</th><th>中文释义</th></tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody>\n\n[59 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774753859635}}
