st-excerpt\">\n                            学习美股相关英语词汇，包括抛售 (Sell-off)、通胀 (Inflation)、暴跌 (Plunged) 等36个核心词汇...\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2026 MingoX | Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages | Powered by Gitee Pages</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"js/main.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774753861276}}
