{"type":"message","id":"6cdd9e08","parentId":"65423353","timestamp":"2026-03-29T03:33:37.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要先登录。让我看看 login 命令的用法，并且检查一下 .edgeone 目录中的配置文件：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✓ 找到 EdgeOne 工具！\n\n**EdgeOne CLI** 已全局安装（`edgeone@1.3.6`），位置：`/usr/bin/edgeone`\n\n**可用命令：**\n```\nedgeone pages deploy [directoryOrZip]  # 部署项目到 EdgeOne Pages\nedgeone pages link                     # 关联项目\nedgeone pages init                     # 初始化项目\nedgeone login                          # 登录（当前未认证）\n```\n\n**当前状态：** 需要先登录才能使用部署功能\n\n---\n\n准备好接收你的 **MX 指令** + 文章/链接 👇"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":294,"output":188,"cacheRead":51072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51554,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774755209890}}
