{"type":"message","id":"8930ea55","parentId":"0705022e","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:05:24.939Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d37c499860eed4ce11228920a61c1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>英语学习：美股新闻 | 英语学习博客</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"通过美股新闻学习英语词汇，包括抛售、通胀、暴跌等金融英语\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"../\" class=\"logo\">🎙️ MingoX</a>\n            <div class=\"nav-links\">\n                <a href=\"../\">首页</a>\n                <a href=\"../about.html\">关于</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <article class=\"post-content\">\n                    <h1>📚 英语学习：美股新闻</h1>\n\n                    <p><strong>US Stock</strong> <span class=\"english-word\">Sell-off</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.抛售）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Devastates</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.重创，现在时）</span> <strong>Tech Giants</strong></p>\n\n                    <p>最近一周，<span class=\"english-word\">Persistent</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.持续的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Inflation</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.通胀）</span>持续 <span class=\"english-word\">Surging</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.飙升，现在分词）</span>，市场 <span class=\"english-word\">Concerned</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.担心的）</span>利率会在更长时间内保持 <span class=\"english-word\">Elevated</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.升高的）</span>。大型科技股遭遇 <span class=\"english-word\">Severe</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.严重的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Setback</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.挫折）</span>，\"美股七巨头\"整体市值累计 <span class=\"english-word\">Evaporated</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.蒸发，过去式）</span>超过 8500 亿美元。</p>\n\n                    <p>Meta 本周 <span class=\"english-word\">Plunged</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.暴跌，过去式）</span>超 11%，创下自 2025 年 10 月以来最差 <span class=\"english-word\">Weekly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.每周的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Performance</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.表现）</span>。此前该公司在一桩 <span class=\"english-word\">Landmark</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.标志性的）</span>社交媒体 <span class=\"english-word\">Lawsuit</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.诉讼案）</span>中败诉。陪审团裁定 Meta 和谷歌 <span class=\"english-word\">Negligent</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.疏忽的）</span>，未能保护平台上的未成年用户。Alphabet 周内 <span class=\"english-word\">Declined</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.下降，过去式）</span>近 9%。</p>\n\n                    <p>微软下跌 6.5%，可能迎来 2008 年以来最差 <span class=\"english-word\">Quarterly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.季度的）</span>表现，软件股受冲击 <span class=\"english-word\">Particularly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adv.特别地）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Severe</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.严重的）</span>。英伟达和亚马逊均下跌约 3%，特斯拉五个交易日内 <span class=\"english-word\">Dropped</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.下跌，过去式）</span>近 2%。</p>\n\n                    <p>此次抛售潮前，Alphabet <span class=\"english-word\">Released</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.发布，过去式）</span>新的研究，公布了一款旨在降低 AI 内存占用的 <span class=\"english-word\">Algorithm</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.算法）</span>，引发 <span class=\"english-word\">Semiconductor</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.半导体）</span>板块 <span class=\"english-word\">Volatility</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.震荡）</span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>受油价 <span class=\"english-word\">Surge</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.飙升）</span>推高 <span class=\"english-word\">Inflationary</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.通胀的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Expectations</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.预期）</span>、债券收益率 <span class=\"english-word\">Rising</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.上升的）</span>影响，成长股本周遭 <span class=\"english-word\">Battered</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.重创，过去式/被动语态）</span>。投资者认为，<span class=\"english-word\">Federal</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.联邦的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Reserve</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.储备）</span>将无法按预期在今年 <span class=\"english-word\">Cut</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.降息，原形）</span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>苹果是\"美股七巨头\"中唯一 <span class=\"english-word\">Modest</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.适度的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Gain</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.涨幅）</span>的个股。报道称，苹果计划将 Siri 语音助手 <span class=\"english-word\">Open</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.开放，原形/不定式）</span>给 ChatGPT 之外的其他 <span class=\"english-word\">Competing</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.竞争的）</span> AI <span class=\"english-word\">Service</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.服务）</span>。</p>\n                </article>\n\n                <!-- 词汇表 -->\n                <div class=\"subtitle\">📖 词汇表</div>\n                <table class=\"vocab-table\">\n                    <thead>\n                        <tr><th>单词</th><th>词性</th><th>中文释义</th></tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody>\n                        <tr><td>Sell-off</td><td>n.</td><td>抛售</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Devastates</td><td>v.</td><td>重创（现在时）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Persistent</td><td>adj.</td><td>持续的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Inflation</td><td>n.</td><td>通胀</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Surging</td><td>v.</td><td>飙升（现在分词）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Concerned</td><td>adj.</td><td>担心的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Elevated</td><td>adj.</td><td>升高的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Severe</td><td>adj.</td><td>严重的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Setback</td><td>n.</td><td>挫折</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Evaporated</td><td>v.</td><td>蒸发（过去式）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Plunged</td><td>v.</td><td>暴跌（过去式）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Weekly</td><td>adj.</td><td>每周的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Performance</td><td>n.</td><td>表现</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Landmark</td><td>adj.</td><td>标志性的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Lawsuit</td><td>n.</td><td>诉讼案</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Negligent</td><td>adj.</td><td>疏忽的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Declined</td><td>v.</td><td>下降（过去式）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Quarterly</td><td>adj.</td><td>季度的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Particularly</td><td>adv.</td><td>特别地</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Dropped</td><td>v.</td><td>下跌（过去式）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Released</td><td>v.</td><td>发布（过去式）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Algorithm</td><td>n.</td><td>算法</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Semiconductor</td><td>n.</td><td>半导体</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Volatility</td><td>n.</td><td>震荡</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Surge</td><td>n.</td><td>飙升</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Inflationary</td><td>adj.</td><td>通胀的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Expectations</td><td>n.</td><td>预期</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Rising</td><td>adj.</td><td>上升的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Battered</td><td>v.</td><td>重创（过去式/被动）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Federal</td><td>adj.</td><td>联邦的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Reserve</td><td>n.</td><td>储备</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Cut</td><td>v.</td><td>降息（原形）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Modest</td><td>adj.</td><td>适度的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Gain</td><td>n.</td><td>涨幅</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Open</td><td>v.</td><td>开放（原形/不定式）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Competing</td><td>adj.</td><td>竞争的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Service</td><td>n.</td><td>服务</td></tr>\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n\n                <!-- 返回链接 -->\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;\">\n                    <a href=\"../\" style=\"color: #667eea; text-decoration: none;\">← 返回首页</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2026 MingoX | Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages | Powered by Gitee Pages</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"../js/main.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774757124935}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e886094","parentId":"8930ea55","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:06:35.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我了解了模板结构。现在我需要创建一个新的 HTML 文件，内容包括：\n\n1. 标题：中国拒绝出席G7峰会，法国警告欧洲市场风险\n2. 双语内容，重点标注词汇\n3. 词汇表\n\n让我创建这个文件。文件名应该是：2026-03-29-china-g7-europe-market.html","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d37c4a58b7188e0dccf7a11cfd3ee","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>英语学习：中欧贸易与G7峰会 | 英语学习博客</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"通过中欧贸易新闻学习英语词汇，包括峰会、拒绝、警告、贸易伙伴等国际关系英语\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"../\" class=\"logo\">🎙️ MingoX</a>\n            <div class=\"nav-links\">\n                <a href=\"../\">首页</a>\n                <a href=\"../about.html\">关于</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <article class=\"post-content\">\n                    <h1>📚 英语学习：中欧贸易与G7峰会</h1>\n\n                    <p><strong>China</strong> <span class=\"english-word\">Refuses</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.拒绝）</span> to <span class=\"english-word\">Attend</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.出席）</span> <strong>G7 Summit</strong>; France <span class=\"english-word\">Issues</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.发出）</span> <strong>Warning</strong>: European Market May Close to China</p>\n\n                    <p>法国外长让-诺埃尔·巴罗在谈及中方拒绝出席G7峰会后公开表态：\"<span class=\"english-word\">China</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Faces</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.面临）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Risk</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.风险）</span> of <span class=\"english-word\">European</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Market</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Closure</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.关闭）</span>.\"</p>\n\n                    <p>原定于今年6月在加拿大举行的G7 <span class=\"english-word\">Summit</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.峰会）</span>，按照惯例，东道主会邀请部分非成员国参会。今年加拿大邀请了中国，但中国已经明确表态，不打算出席G7峰会。</p>\n\n                    <p>过去几年，G7对中国的态度，从南海到台海，从贸易到技术 <span class=\"english-word\">Sanctions</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.制裁）</span>，年年峰会年年谈中国，谈完之后发个 <span class=\"english-word\">Communiqué</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.公报）</span>，措辞一年比一年强硬。中国拒绝出席，法国的反应比其他国家更强烈。</p>\n\n                    <p>巴罗说：\"如果中国不遵守 <span class=\"english-word\">International</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.国际的）</span> 规则，那么欧洲市场对中国商品的开放，就不可能继续 <span class=\"english-word\">Taken for Granted</span><span class=\"word-info\">（phrase.理所当然）</span>。\"</p>\n\n                    <p>2024年，中欧 <span class=\"english-word\">Trade</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Volume</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.贸易总额）</span> 超过 7800 亿欧元。中国是欧盟第二大贸易伙伴，仅次于美国，欧盟是中国第一大贸易伙伴。</p>\n\n                    <p>再看法国，2024年中法贸易额突破800亿欧元，中国是法国在亚洲最大的贸易伙伴。法国对华出口的主要商品，包括 <span class=\"english-word\">Luxury</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Goods</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.奢侈品）</span>、农产品、<span class=\"english-word\">Aviation</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Equipment</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.航空设备）</span>、<span class=\"english-word\">Cosmetics</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.化妆品）</span>，每一个都是法国的 <span class=\"english-word\">Pillar</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Industry</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.支柱产业）</span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>欧盟的贸易 <span class=\"english-word\">Policy</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.政策）</span>，决定权在欧洲委员会，不是法国单方面说了算。就算法国想在欧盟内部推动对华市场关闭，也必经过德国、荷兰、意大利等欧盟国家的同意。</p>\n\n                    <p>但德国车企、荷兰 <span class=\"english-word\">Lithography</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Machine</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.光刻机）</span>、意大利制造业，哪一家愿意放弃中国市场？2023年，德国对华 <span class=\"english-word\">Direct</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Investment</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.直接投资）</span> 高达119亿欧元，创下历史新高。</p>\n\n                    <p>法国之所以放这种 <span class=\"english-word\">Tough</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Talk</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.狠话）</span>，明眼人都看得出来，这是欧洲国家惯用的 <span class=\"english-word\">Negotiation</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Tactic</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.谈判策略）</span>。G7峰会还没开，中方已经拒绝出席，这让西方国家的面子多少有点挂不住了。</p>\n\n                    <p>作为欧洲主要大国，法国需要在舆论场上把 <span class=\"english-word\">Stance</span><span class=\"english-word\">Taken</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.姿态）</span>做足，至少让外界看起来，是中方不配合，不是我们没给机会。</p>\n\n                    <p>姿态归姿态，实际动作是另一回事。法国外长发表言论后，法国外交部官网还发布了一份 <span class=\"english-word\">Statement</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.声明）</span>，强调与中国保持 <span class=\"english-word\">Dialogue</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Channel</span> <span class=\"word-info\">（n.对话渠道）</span> 畅通的重要性。</p>\n\n                    <p>同一时间，法国总统外事顾问正在与中方进行 <span class=\"english-word\">Diplomatic</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Consultation</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.外交磋商）</span>，讨论的内容包括 <span class=\"english-word\">Climate</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Change</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.气候变化）</span>、全球 <span class=\"english-word\">Supply</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Chain</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Stability</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.供应链稳定）</span> 等，这些议题，哪一个离得开与中国合作？</p>\n\n                    <p>如果真要谈市场关闭，我们不妨看看谁更需要谁。中国对欧出口的主力产品，是 <span class=\"english-word\">Electromechanical</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Equipment</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.机电设备）</span>、<span class=\"english-word\">Photovoltaic</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Components</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.光伏组件）</span>、<span class=\"english-word\">Electric</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Vehicles</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.电动汽车）</span>、<span class=\"english-word\">Consumer</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Electronics</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.消费电子）</span>，这些东西，欧洲短期内找不到 <span class=\"english-word\">Alternative</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Source</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.替代来源）</span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>2024年，欧盟从中国进口的电动汽车超过50万辆，占到欧盟电动车总进口量的四成以上。谈市场关闭，欧洲消费者怎么办？本土产能补得上吗？</p>\n\n                    <p>反过来，欧洲对华出口的主力，是高端制造、奢侈品、农产品，这些东西，中国同样可以 <span class=\"english-word\">Shift</span> <span class=\"english-word\">to</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Other</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Markets</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.转向其他市场）</span>。空客飞机不是只有欧洲能造，奢侈品消费也不是只靠中国，但失去中国这个全球最大的增量市场，欧洲企业将会面临巨大损失。</p>\n\n                    <p><span class=\"english-word\">Time</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Window</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.时间窗口）</span>。欧洲经济目前处在高 <span class=\"english-word\">Inflation</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.通胀）</span>、低增长的泥潭里，德国连续两年经济零增长，法国公共债务占GDP比重超过110%，这时候谈关闭中国市场，不是在 <span class=\"english-word\">Bite</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Off</span> <span class=\"english-word\">More</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Than</span> <span class=\"english-word\">One</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Can</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Chew</span><span class=\"word-info\">（phrase.自讨苦吃）</span> 吗？</p>\n\n                    <p>巴罗发言后的24小时内，法国 CAC40 指数中，对华出口占比高的几家公司股价小幅 <span class=\"english-word\">Fluctuate</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.波动）</span>，随后法国紧急表态后，才趋于稳定。</p>\n                </article>\n\n                <!-- 词汇表 -->\n                <div class=\"subtitle\">📖 词汇表</div>\n                <table class=\"vocab-table\">\n                    <thead>\n                        <tr><th>单词</th><th>词性</th><th>中文释义</th></tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody>\n                        <tr><td>Refuses</td><td>v.</td><td>拒绝（第三人称单数）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Attend</td><td>v.</td><td>出席</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Issues</td><td>v.</td><td>发出（第三人称单数）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Warning</td><td>n.</td><td>警告</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Summit</td><td>n.</td><td>峰会</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Sanctions</td><td>n.</td><td>制裁（复数）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Communiqué</td><td>n.</td><td>公报</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>International</td><td>adj.</td><td>国际的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Taken for Granted</td><td>phrase.</td><td>理所当然</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Trade Volume</td><td>n.</td><td>贸易总额</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Luxury Goods</td><td>n.</td><td>奢侈品</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Aviation Equipment</td><td>n.</td><td>航空设备</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Cosmetics</td><td>n.</td><td>化妆品</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Pillar Industry</td><td>n.</td><td>支柱产业</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Policy</td><td>n.</td><td>政策</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Lithography Machine</td><td>n.</td><td>光刻机</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Direct Investment</td><td>n.</td><td>直接投资</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Tough Talk</td><td>n.</td><td>狠话</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Negotiation Tactic</td><td>n.</td><td>谈判策略</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Stance Taken</td><td>n.</td><td>姿态</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Statement</td><td>n.</td><td>声明</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Dialogue Channel</td><td>n.</td><td>对话渠道</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Diplomatic Consultation</td><td>n.</td><td>外交磋商</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Climate Change</td><td>n.</td><td>气候变化</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Supply Chain Stability</td><td>n.</td><td>供应链稳定</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Electromechanical Equipment</td><td>n.</td><td>机电设备</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Photovoltaic Components</td><td>n.</td><td>光伏组件</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Electric Vehicles</td><td>n.</td><td>电动汽车</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Consumer Electronics</td><td>n.</td><td>消费电子</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Alternative Source</td><td>n.</td><td>替代来源</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Shift to Other Markets</td><td>v.</td><td>转向其他市场</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Time Window</td><td>n.</td><td>时间窗口</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Inflation</td><td>n.</td><td>通胀</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Bite Off More Than One Can Chew</td><td>phrase.</td><td>自讨苦吃/贪多嚼不烂</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Fluctuate</td><td>v.</td><td>波动</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Faces</td><td>v.</td><td>面临（第三人称单数）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Risk</td><td>n.</td><td>风险</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>European Market Closure</td><td>n.</td><td>欧洲市场关闭</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>China</td><td>n.</td><td>中国</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Market</td><td>n.</td><td>市场</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Closure</td><td>n.</td><td>关闭</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Europe</td><td>n.</td><td>欧洲</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>French</td><td>adj.</td><td>法国的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Foreign Minister</td><td>n.</td><td>外长</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Canada</td><td>n.</td><td>加拿大</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Host</td><td>n.</td><td>东道主</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Non-member</td><td>n.</td><td>非成员国</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>South China Sea</td><td>n.</td><td>南海</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Taiwan Strait</td><td>n.</td><td>台海</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Trade</td><td>n.</td><td>贸易</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Technology</td><td>n.</td><td>技术</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>G7</td><td>n.</td><td>七国集团</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Attitude</td><td>n.</td><td>态度</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Rules</td><td>n.</td><td>规则</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Open</td><td>adj.</td><td>开放的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Continue</td><td>v.</td><td>继续</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>European Union (EU)</td><td>n.</td><td>欧盟</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>United States (US)</td><td>n.</td><td>美国</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Germany</td><td>n.</td><td>德国</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>France</td><td>n.</td><td>法国</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Netherlands</td><td>n.</td><td>荷兰</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Italy</td><td>n.</td><td>意大利</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Export</td><td>v./n.</td><td>出口</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Asian</td><td>adj.</td><td>亚洲的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Pillar</td><td>n.</td><td>支柱</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Industry</td><td>n.</td><td>产业</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Decision-making Power</td><td>n.</td><td>决定权</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>European Commission</td><td>n.</td><td>欧洲委员会</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Unilateral</td><td>adj.</td><td>单方面的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Push</td><td>v.</td><td>推动</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Agreement</td><td>n.</td><td>同意</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Automobile</td><td>n.</td><td>汽车</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Give up</td><td>v.</td><td>放弃</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Record</td><td>n./adj.</td><td>记录/创纪录的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Obvious</td><td>adj.</td><td>明显的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>European</td><td>adj.</td><td>欧洲的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Common</td><td>adj.</td><td>常见的/共同的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Negotiation</td><td>n.</td><td>谈判</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Strategy</td><td>n.</td><td>策略</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Face</td><td>n.</td><td>面子</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Major Power</td><td>n.</td><td>大国</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Public Opinion</td><td>n.</td><td>舆论</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Outward</td><td>adv./adj.</td><td>向外/外部的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Make Sufficient Effort</td><td>v.</td><td>做足</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>At least</td><td>adv.</td><td>至少</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Outsider</td><td>n.</td><td>外界</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Cooperate</td><td>v.</td><td>配合</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Opportunity</td><td>n.</td><td>机会</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Actual</td><td>adj.</td><td>实际的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Action</td><td>n.</td><td>行动</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Matter</td><td>n.</td><td>事情</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Official Website</td><td>n.</td><td>官网</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Release</td><td>v.</td><td>发布</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Emphasize</td><td>v.</td><td>强调</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Maintain</td><td>v.</td><td>保持</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>Unimpeded</td><td>adj.</td><td>畅通的</td></tr>\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n\n                <!-- 返回链接 -->\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;\">\n                    <a href=\"../\" style=\"color: #667eea; text-decoration: none;\">← 返回首页</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2026 MingoX | Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages | Powered by Gitee Pages</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"../js/main.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n","file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/posts/2026-03-29-china-g7-europe-market.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":2986,"output":5156,"cacheRead":52992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61134,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774757124940}}
