{"type":"message","id":"cdcd1466","parentId":"53610c59","timestamp":"2026-03-29T04:07:55.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有存储的凭据。我需要告诉用户需要配置 Gitee 访问令牌，或者让我生成一个临时的推送命令。\n\n不过，既然这是一个演示流程，我可以：\n1. 告诉用户需要配置 Gitee 访问令牌\n2. 提供推送命令\n3. 继续下一步（edgeone 部署）\n\n或者，我可以询问用户是否有 Gitee 访问令牌。\n\n让我告诉用户需要配置认证。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**⚠️ Git 推送需要认证**\n\n代码已提交到本地仓库，但推送到 Gitee 需要配置访问令牌。\n\n**选项 1：配置环境变量**\n```bash\nexport GITEE_TOKEN=\"你的Gitee访问令牌\"\n```\n\n**选项 2：手动推送**\n```bash\ncd /workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news\ngit push https://<access_token>@gitee.com/siglea/news.git\n```\n\n**获取 Gitee 访问令牌：**\n1. 访问 https://gitee.com/profile/personal_access_tokens\n2. 创建新的个人访问令牌（选择 `projects` 权限）\n3. 复制令牌（只显示一次）\n\n---\n\n**当前进度：**\n- ✅ 文章已生成：`posts/2026-03-29-china-g7-europe-market.html`\n- ✅ 首页已更新\n- ✅ 本地 Git 已提交\n- ⏳ 等待推送认证...\n\n你有 Gitee 访问令牌吗？提供后我可以继续推送和部署。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":149,"output":445,"cacheRead":63232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63826,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774757268801}}
