{"type":"message","id":"66729cb1","parentId":"f45976d5","timestamp":"2026-03-29T07:33:59.757Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求后续收到 MX 指令后：\n1. 先拉取仓库最新代码\n2. 检查仓库内的 README.md 的最新要求\n3. 按照最新要求来生成新的内容\n\n然后给了新的 MX 指令：\nMX https://www.toutiao.com/article/7622476513778090559/?log_from=e01f2660f1bcf_1774769503719\n\n我需要：\n1. 先 git pull 拉取最新代码\n2. 读取 README.md 查看最新要求\n3. 获取文章内容\n4. 按照要求生成内容\n5. 提交、推送、部署\n\n让我开始执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来测试这个新流程："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d38838ab90cbcb9e56b16001eddd6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news && git pull origin master 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d38838c54cd1d2329e9b7722a1460","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d38838e3a768544e61bc475881069","name":"coze_web_fetch","arguments":{"urls":"https://www.toutiao.com/article/7622476513778090559/?log_from=e01f2660f1bcf_1774769503719"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":81902,"output":429,"cacheRead":34048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116379,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774769623010}}
