{"type":"message","id":"2a78cee0","parentId":"60c1f377","timestamp":"2026-03-29T13:37:29.818Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功！新的链接已经生成了。让我把这个新链接提供给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ 已重新部署成功！获取新链接\n\n### 🔄 执行结果\n\n| 步骤 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 1. 重新部署到 EdgeOne Pages | ✅ 成功 |\n\n---\n\n### 🌐 新的访问链接\n\n**EdgeOne Pages（带有效参数）：**\n```\nhttps://mingox-dzlbtybw.edgeone.cool?eo_token=3f37968499133128146a645c178954d4&eo_time=1774791439\n```\n\n**链接包含的参数：**\n- `eo_token`: 临时访问令牌\n- `eo_time`: 有效时间戳\n\n**控制台链接：**\n```\nhttps://console.cloud.tencent.com/edgeone/pages/project/pages-7lkihc9fgyl/deployment/pghuvt4n2t\n```\n\n---\n\n### 💡 关于 401 错误\n\n之前链接返回 401 UNAUTHORIZED 的原因是：\n- `eo_time` 参数中的时间戳已过期\n- EdgeOne 使用临时令牌机制，链接有时间限制\n\n**解决方法：**\n- 重新部署（已执行）获取新的有效链接\n- 或者访问控制台查看部署状态\n\n---\n\n**新的访问链接已生成，现在应该可以正常访问了！** ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1539,"output":315,"cacheRead":158528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":160382,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774791440634}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d3230ee","parentId":"2a78cee0","timestamp":"2026-03-29T13:46:24.824Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-29 21:37:19 GMT+8] Exec completed (young-la, code 0) :: y! To view your project's live URL. EDGEONE_DEPLOY_URL=https://mingox-dzlbtybw.edgeone.cool?eo_token=3f37968499133128146a645c178954d4&eo_time=1774791439 EDGEONE_DEPLOY_TYPE=preset…\nSystem: [2026-03-29 21:46:24 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 申广亮 (ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb) [msg:om_x100b53a69c3840a4c44719a9eebd00c]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53a69c3840a4c44719a9eebd00c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb\",\n  \"sender\": \"申广亮\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-29 21:46 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"申广亮 (ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb\",\n  \"name\": \"申广亮\"\n}\n```\n\n你在干啥"}],"timestamp":1774791984815}}
{"type":"message","id":"43a4d6d3","parentId":"7d3230ee","timestamp":"2026-03-29T13:46:42.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问我\"你在干啥\"。\n\n这是一个简单的对话询问，我应该简洁地回答我最近在做什么。根据会话历史，我刚刚完成了：\n\n1. 帮助用户建立了 MingoX 项目（多语言多媒体内容平台）\n2. 克隆了 Gitee 仓库\n3. 按照用户提供的 MX 指令生成双语学习文章\n4. 提交代码并推送到 Gitee\n5. 部署到 EdgeOne Pages\n6. 配置了自动化流程，包括：\n   - 令牌持久化存储\n   - 自动加载配置\n   - 验证脚本\n   - 完整的文档\n\n我应该简洁地总结一下最近完成的工作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"最近在帮你搭建和运营 **MingoX** 项目（多语言多媒体内容平台）：\n\n1. **建立了项目目录** - 克隆了 Gitee 仓库\n2. **配置了自动化流程** - 保存了 Gitee 和 EdgeOne 令牌，实现了：\n   - Git 自动推送（无需输入密码）\n   - EdgeOne 一键部署\n3. **生成了 6 篇双语文章** - 关于财经、科技、AI、国际关系等主题\n4. **部署到双站点** - Gitee Pages + EdgeOne Pages\n5. **建立了新工作流** - 收到 MX 指令自动生成内容 → 推送 → 部署\n\n刚才刚刚重新部署获取了新的访问链接。\n\n现在站点已经完全运行起来了，你可以发送：\n- `MX [文章链接]` - 生成新内容并部署\n- `MX deploy` - 拉取最新代码并重新部署\n\n需要我继续做什么吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":126711,"output":517,"cacheRead":34176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":161404,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774791984821}}
