{"type":"message","id":"0dad3d92","parentId":"8eb0fb45","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:15:34.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是否可以调用浏览器打开飞书文档，或者识别图片内的文字。\n\n让我检查可用的工具：\n\n1. `canvas` 工具 - 可以用于打开网页并截图识别\n2. `image` 工具 - 可以分析图片中的文字\n3. `coze_web_fetch` - 已经尝试过，只能获取部分内容\n\n让我尝试使用 canvas 工具打开网页并截图，然后用 image 工具识别文字。\n\n这个思路是可行的。我需要：\n1. 使用 canvas 工具打开网页\n2. 截图\n3. 使用 image 工具识别图片中的文字\n\n不过，这种方法需要：\n- 浏览器支持（我当前环境中可能没有浏览器或无法显示）\n- JavaScript 支持（canvas 工具可能需要 JavaScript 执行能力）\n\n让我先尝试 canvas 工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以尝试！让我使用浏览器工具打开文档并识别文字："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3a2a22c865b4fd638b460bf6843b","name":"canvas","arguments":{"action":"present","url":"https://my.feishu.cn/docx/FpApdl5qyoRpnjxJT5AcxyScnBh","width":1280,"height":1024}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":131055,"output":418,"cacheRead":41536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":173009,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774797311910}}
