{"type":"message","id":"42747232","parentId":"5c83ac8e","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:23:42.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，文章文件已生成。现在需要更新首页，将新文章添加到列表中。按照 README.md 的新规范：\n\n1. 标题要逐字一致，包括英文副标题用 <small> 标签包裹\n2. 标题和内容分别添加超链接\n3. meta 信息不添加链接\n4. 英文副标题需要换行显示\n\n标题：📝 AI创作黄金10条 | AI Creation Golden Rules: 10 Ways to Stand Out\n\n标签：📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 文字 | 🏷️ AI, 内容创作\n\n摘要：AI创作时代，如何让你的内容脱颖而出？这10条黄金法则，帮你打造爆款内容！","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3a319a008ce0e6d17f9324e660ce","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":131833,"output":327,"cacheRead":42048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":174208,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774797806643}}
{"type":"message","id":"cceac7fb","parentId":"42747232","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:23:42.825Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d3a319a008ce0e6d17f9324e660ce","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover\">\n    <title>MingoX - Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"MingoX - 多语言多媒体内容平台，用文字、图片、播客等形式分享新闻、思想与见解。Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"./\" class=\"logo\">🎙️ MingoX</a>\n            <div class=\"nav-links\">\n                <a href=\"./\">首页</a>\n                <a href=\"./about.html\">关于</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <div class=\"site-intro\">\n                    <h1>🎙️ MingoX</h1>\n                    <p class=\"site-tagline\">Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages</p>\n                    <p class=\"site-desc\">用文字、图片、播客等多种形式，分享新闻、思想与见解</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <h2 class=\"page-title\">📰 最新发布</h2>\n\n                <ul class=\"post-list\">\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-gold-price-analysis.html\">\n                                💰 金价跌破4500：联储按兵不动与4月回调风险 <small class=\"title-en\">Gold Below $4,500: Fed on Hold & April Pullback Risk</small>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 财经, 投资分析</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\