{"type":"message","id":"c415e31c","parentId":"62b56d6f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:26:58.364Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"飞书的 emoji_type 需要具体的 emoji 名称（大写），不是 UPPERCASE。\n\n让我使用正确的飞书 emoji type。常见的有：\n- THUMBSUP\n- OK\n- THANKS\n- SMILE\n- BLUSH\n- PARTY\n- JOY\n- PRAY\n- CONGRATS\n- STAR\n- EYE_ROLL\n\n我使用 THUMBSUP，这是\"👍\" 对应的飞书 emoji。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3a349368f623423fc0fda9de7d46","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"react","channel":"feishu","emoji_type":"THUMBSUP","target":"user:ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":20223,"output":255,"cacheRead":160768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":181246,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774798010805}}
