{"type":"message","id":"1122631d","parentId":"59cbb9ba","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:27:06.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"飞书的 react 动作不支持 emoji_type 参数。我应该使用 message 工具的 emoji 选项。但 message 工具的 emoji 参数可能只支持 UPPERCASE 格式。\n\n让我试试直接用 message 发送带表情的消息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3a34afd8a1d02a0cc095efa02379","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","target":"user:ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb","message":"👍 已帮你识别图片文字并生成了新文章！这是腾讯研究院的深度研究报告，分析了老年人AI学习的六大类型、学习动因和课程标准。关键洞察：老年人学习AI不只是\"老有所学\"的生活点缀，而是关系到银发力量能否被有效赋能的基础性议题。分层教学、连续陪伴、安全培育是课程设计的核心。"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":217,"output":232,"cacheRead":181120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":181569,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774798021989}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ad3647b","parentId":"1122631d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:27:07.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"👍 已帮你识别图片文字并生成了新文章！这是腾讯研究院的深度研究报告，分析了老年人AI学习的六大类型、学习动因和课程标准。关键洞察：老年人学习AI不只是\"老有所学\"的生活点缀，而是关系到银发力量能否被有效赋能的基础性议题。分层教学、连续陪伴、安全培育是课程设计的核心。"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774798027497}}
